'''''The Humongous Book of Dinosaurs''''' is a large [[dinosaur]] book for [[Children's literature|children]] published in 1997 by [[Abrams Books|Stewart, Tabori, & Chang Publishers]].<ref name="NYDailyNews">{{cite web | url=http://articles.nydailynews.com/1997-05-20/entertainment/18033445_1_dinosaurs-science-of-jurassic-park-postage-stamps | title=Turning Up The Volumes On Dinos Publishers Book Their Seats On The 'Lost World' Express |website=www.nydailynews.com | publisher=''New York Daily News'' | accessdate=May 17, 2012}} * {{cite web | url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/orlandosentinel/access/78593934.html?dids=78593934:78593934&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=May+25%2C+1997&author=&pub=Orlando+Sentinel&desc=BOOK+BUZZ&pqatl=google | title=Book Buzz | publisher=''Orlando Sentinel'' | date=May 25, 1997 | accessdate=May 17, 2012}}</ref> It has 1,256 pages.<ref name="NYDailyNews"/>

